title: Top Dishes From Around the World in 2025
description: Kate Krader, Bloomberg News food editor, tells Carol Massar on Bloomberg Markets that Indian cuisine has surged in quality and prominence in New York over the past few years, standing out among the world’s top dishes. (Source: Bloomberg)
